show.description: Like A Dragon follows a carefree county magistrate who is revealed to be a legendary prodigy in a chaotic era, using wit and modern knowledge to transform a small county into a thriving empire. It blends historical intrigue with unexpected twists, showcasing his journey of growth and triumph amidst adversity.
